#~ "<option>--with-ooo-dir</option>=<filename class=\"directory\">/usr/lib/"
#~ "openoffice</filename> <option>--with-ooo-sdk-dir</option>=<filename class="
#~ "\"directory\">/usr/lib/openoffice/SDK</filename></userinput>\n"
#~ "</screen> You'll need to use the correct locations of the OpenOffice.org "
#~ "libraries and SDK, of course."
